        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         depends on what your after in the zone</P><P>are you questing ?, <BR>for armor?, flowers?,<BR>or just for fun/xp?</P><P><BR>figure out what you want, the target the mobs that best suit that</P><P>pom is way different from other zones, in alot of regards<BR>generally speaking of killing, the mobs here have more hp than mobs of there lvl anywhere else(as far as i know), its insane to have 10k+ lvl40mobs etc..</P><P>so its not as simple to kill shit here as other places, and also, anything worht killing(quest wise) is 55+, so fearing isnt an option<BR>thers no undead in zone, so cant charm/DC/slow anything either(druids/chanters can tear up here with DC pets)</P><P>this is a good writeup on targetting high end zone questing/xp, speically speaking, puppets and alice4 mobs , the techniques i listed above trasnlate throught the zone as well(i also do alot of mobs with pet tanking + bond/pact), </P><P>my suggestion is, ifnd out what you want from the zone, then spend some time exploring, screw maps, just look around, or if tehres anyone there, ask em for a tour<BR>after you experience the zone for a bit(talk to npcs etc..), look up a beastiarity/map and go from there onto kiling mobs</P><P>personally, i started iwth fear kiting in maze/forest, and worked my way up that way, trying new shit all over(mobs and tecnhiques)</P><P>now all i do is root/dot + summoning, well,i suppose thats the best way to describe it<BR>since all i do is hunt for throne cards, i only fihgt mobs this way(with puppets just being a modified versoin)<BR>anything worth killing summons here, so you gotta fear(not really applicable), root/dot + summon, hate kite(this , in my expeience here dosnt work as well as root/dot), pet tank, etc...</P><P>if oyu have any speciric questoins for me, log onto veeshan and shoot me a tell, or just as here on the board, ill gladly help inasmuch as i can</P><P>Lich Kriista Silence<BR>Warlock of Veeshan</P><P><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?nu